s every 8 hours at 00:00, 08:00, and 16:00 UTC, based on the premium between perpetual and index prices. The exchange uses a time-weighted average price methodology with a ±0.05% cap on funding rates. Positions held during funding times automatically pay or receive funding based on long/short positioning and current market sentiment."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
